"```sql\nSELECT posts.Id, posts.OwnerDisplayName\nFROM posts\nWHERE YEAR(posts.CreationDate) = 2010\nORDER BY posts.FavoriteCount DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `Id` and `OwnerDisplayName` of the post with the highest `FavoriteCount` from the year 2010. It orders the results by `FavoriteCount` in descending order and limits the output to the top result, which corresponds to the most valuable post according to the given evidence."